Privacy Policy for Eva AI Assistant

Last Updated: 24/10/24

At Strijder AI, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how Eva, our AI assistant, manages your data and interactions with OpenAI agents and other specialized agents.

1. Information We Collect
Eva may collect the following information:

Personal Information: This includes any information you provide when interacting with Eva, such as your name, email address, and preferences.
Usage Data: Information on how you interact with Eva and the specialized agents, including tasks, queries, and agent configurations.
Communication Data: Data from emails, task requests, voice interactions, or other communications that Eva handles for you.
2. How We Use Your Information
The information collected is used to:

Enhance Eva’s ability to manage tasks, agents, and workflows based on user preferences.
Improve the personalization of the AI experience by learning from interactions.
Optimize how Eva delegates tasks to specialized agents to streamline efficiency.
Train models for better predictions and recommendations, using anonymized data where applicable.
3. Data Sharing
We do not sell your personal data. However, Eva may share your data with:

OpenAI Agents: When interacting with OpenAI’s tools (such as GPT-based models), data may be shared with OpenAI for processing tasks and providing responses.
Third-party service providers: For functions like cloud storage, data analytics, or specific APIs Eva relies on to assist with your requests.
4. Data Security
We implement security measures to protect your information, including:

Encryption of data during transmission and at rest.
Secure access to data and user interactions via authenticated systems.
However, while we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your data, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.

5. User Control Over Data
You have the right to:

Access: Request access to the personal data Eva has collected.
Correction: Update or correct your information at any time.
Deletion: Request deletion of your personal data.
Withdraw Consent: You can choose to stop providing data by discontinuing use of Eva at any time.
6. Use of OpenAI Services
Eva may interact with OpenAI agents to assist with tasks such as:

Text generation and conversation.
Language translation and summarization.
Content generation and automated responses.
When Eva communicates with OpenAI, your queries may be processed by OpenAI’s API. For more details on how OpenAI handles your data, please refer to OpenAI’s privacy policy.

7. Updates to the Privacy Policy
We may update this policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. Any updates will be posted on this page, and we will notify you of significant changes.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how your data is managed, please contact us at:

Email: strijderai@gmail.com
